%% Mermaid flowchart describing the prototype topology
flowchart LR
  CLI["CLI Agent"] -->|submit restore| MySQLQueue[(MySQL Queue)]
  CLI -->|status query| MySQLQueue
  Daemon["Daemon"] -->|poll queued jobs| MySQLQueue
  Daemon -->|download backup| S3[(AWS S3<br/>Cross-Account)]
  Daemon -->|restore + post-SQL| MySQLTarget[(MySQL 8 Host)]
  Daemon -->|emit events| MySQLQueue
  Daemon -->|metrics + logs| Observability[(Datadog)]
  MySQLQueue -->|configuration| CLI
  MySQLQueue -->|status| Daemon
  CLI -.->|AWS credentials<br/>via profile| AWSProfile[AWS Profile<br/>+ Parameter Store]
  Daemon -.->|AWS credentials<br/>via profile| AWSProfile
